<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">嗨～<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你发现了吗～？<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />昨天<delay20 />从<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />家<delay20 />
飘出了一阵<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />的香味呢～</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />没错，<delay20 />我昨天确实<delay8 />
是在家里制作点心哦。<delay20 />
<20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过真亏你能猜到我做的是<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />呢。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">诶嘿～<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />可不要小瞧了<delay20 />
我的鼻子哦～<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要是<tag a="135" b="7" arg="0xcd00" />的香味，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管离得多远，<delay20 />
我都能闻出来～！<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，你真厉害<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" /><10_4 />
<20_2 arg="8" /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这次我尝试在配料上<delay20 />
下了点功夫哦。<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是稍微动了动手，<delay20 />
看上去就特别华丽，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可以说是“连外观都很美味”呢！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶～？<delay20 />外观也分好吃和不好吃的吗～？！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />只是看看就能觉得很好吃的话，<delay20 />
那东西就永远不会被吃完了呢～<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真好～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />诶～？<delay20 />光看着就能知道很好吃的话～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />是不是<delay8 />
肚子就更饿了呀～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay20 />如果闻着好吃，<delay20 />
看着也好吃的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />是不是尝起来就更好吃了呢～？！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">呵呵，<delay20 />那下次我就<delay20 />
为<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你<delay20 />
用心制作一份吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不讲究外观，<delay20 />普通的就可以了。<delay20 />
你快点给我做一份吧～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />毕竟光靠感觉，<delay20 />是填不饱肚子的～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="TakenAback" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />唉～</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">嗨～<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有没有什么书可以推荐给我的呀～？</message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦？！<delay frames="40" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />
你要读书吗？<delay frames="40" />
真令人意外。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想，<delay frames="40" />虽然我不知道你有什么喜好，<delay20 />
不过要说给我留下印象的<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />》<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />和《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd01" />》。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯～嗯～<delay20 />我知道了～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，<delay20 />这两本书<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哪一本比较厚呢～？<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">哇，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看来你是认真的呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要说哪一本更厚的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />》。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />内容非常充实，十分引人入胜哦！</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">啊！<delay20 />你搞错了～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是想，估计我看不了多久就会睡着的，<delay20 />
所以想挑一本更适合做枕头的呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样啊。<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />》<delay20 />
拿来当成枕头应该也非常合适吧。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要拿来当成枕头的话，<delay20 />我比较推荐
《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd01" />》哦。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嘿～<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />～<delay frames="40" />
来和我一起唱歌吧～<delay frames="80" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啦～<delay20 />啦～<delay8 />啦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在外面唱歌实在太难为情了，<delay20 />
我可办不到！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过<delay8 />刚才那句“<tag a="110" b="5" />”<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你的口头禅对吧？<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得非常适合你唱的歌，<delay20 />听起来很棒哦！<anim id="Aha" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的吗～？<delay frames="40" />谢谢～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，<delay20 />你也说这句口头禅吧～<delay20 />
说不定就不害羞了呢～？<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">是、<delay20 />是这样吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然你这么说了，<delay20 />我就来试试看吧。<delay frames="80" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，<delay20 />咳<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />啦～<delay20 />啦哩～<delay8 />啦～<delay20 />
噜～<delay20 />啦～<delay20 />啦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="205" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Clapping" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay20 />真好听～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />歌唱得好听，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />口头禅也很适合你哦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Shocked" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="206" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">真的吗？！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />我好开心！<delay frames="40" />
难得你的好意，<delay20 />
我今后就继续用这个口头禅啦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>